<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Book Your Place | Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">

</head>

<body>

<!-- ================= NAVBAR ================= -->
<%- include("../partials/navbar") %>


<!-- ================= HERO SECTION ================= -->
<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
        <h1>Find Your Perfect Stay</h1>
        <p>
            Experience seamless room booking with Book Your Place — 
            your trusted platform for discovering comfortable, 
            stylish, and affordable accommodations.
            Browse premium stays, explore modern rooms,
            and enjoy a curated selection of spaces designed
            to fit every travel mood, purpose, and budget. 
            Whether you’re planning a vacation, a weekend getaway,
            or a business trip, we help you find the perfect stay
            with ease, comfort, and complete transparency.
        </p>

<a href="http://localhost:3000/book"><button class="explore-btn">Explore Rooms</button></a> 
    </div>

    <div class="hero-img">
        <img src="/images/HomePage.webp" alt="homepage">
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= FEATURES SECTION ================= -->
<section class="features">

    <h2>Why Choose Book Your Place?</h2>

    <div class="feature-grid">

        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Secure Booking</h3>
            <p>Your information stays encrypted and safe throughout the booking process.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Premium Stays</h3>
            <p>Carefully selected hotels and rooms to give you comfort & value.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Instant Confirmation</h3>
            <p>No delays. Your booking is confirmed the moment you click.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <section class="how-it-works">
    <h2>How It Works</h2>

    <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
            <h3>Search</h3>
            <p>Find rooms in your preferred location with ease.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-hotel"></i>
            <h3>Select</h3>
            <p>Choose from verified listings and premium stays.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-credit-card"></i>
            <h3>Book</h3>
            <p>Make secure bookings instantly with one click.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

</section>
<section class="about-section">
    <h2>About Book Your Place</h2>
    <p>
        Book Your Place is designed to make finding your ideal stay simple, fast, and stress-free.
        Whether you're planning a weekend getaway, a business trip, or a long vacation,
        we connect you with comfortable, affordable, and premium-quality rooms across multiple locations.
    </p>

    <p>
        Our mission is to help you discover the perfect place to stay — with secure booking,
        transparent pricing, and smooth navigation. With a curated selection of rooms
        and verified listings, we aim to bring comfort and trust to every journey.
    </p>

    <p>
        From modern hotels to cozy stays, Book Your Place ensures a seamless experience
        from browsing to booking. Your comfort, your choice — Book Your Place.
    </p>
</section>



<!-- ================= FOOTER ================= -->
<%- include("../partials/footer")%>


<script>
    const menuIcon = document.getElementById('menuIcon');
    const navLinks = document.getElementById('navLinks');

    menuIcon.addEventListener('click', () => {
        navLinks.classList.toggle('active');
    });
</script>

</body>
</html>
